          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-6 col-lg-3 select">
              <i class="fa fa-user-plus" aria-hidden="true"></i>
              <div>
                <h5 class="h4">Sign Up Online</h5>
                <p>
                  Signing up is easy. Simply click the button below and fill out
                  the form. When you do, a member of our team will reach out to
                  you with next steps.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-6 col-lg-3 select">
              <i class="fa fa-file-text" aria-hidden="true"></i>
              <div>
                <h5 class="h4">Share documents</h5>
                <p>
                  After signing up, we will require you to share some documents
                  with us. These documents are typically your drivers license -
                  a valid one, your academic certificates and possibly, a
                  guarantor.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-6 col-lg-3 select">
              <i class="fa fa-users" aria-hidden="true"></i>
              <div>
                <h5 class="h4">Schedule screening</h5>
                <p>
                  When this is done, we will schedule a screening session with
                  you. This typically lasts anywhere between a couple of hours
                  to a few days. We really want to get to know you personally,
                  so feel free to talk to us.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-6 col-lg-3 select">
              <i class="fa fa-mobile fa-lg" aria-hidden="true"></i>
              <div>
                <h4 class="h4">Get the app and go</h4>
                <p>
                  We will complete the process from our end — assign you a
                  vehicle and a route — You will then download the driver's and
                  get ready to make your first trip. Congratulations, welcome to
                  the family.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
